# NOTE: unlike .gitignore, .dockerignore patterns are anchored to the build
# context root — nested paths need the **/ prefix. Without it, the API key in
# backend/ai-service-python/.env would be baked into the image.
**/.env
**/.venv
**/node_modules
**/__pycache__
**/*.db
**/*.log
**/tests
.git
docs
demo-pages
eval
benchmark
loader
extension
